xray [option] target           # scan target with specified rules
'option' can be:
    --js                       # scan javascript files only
    --css                      # scan css files only
    --html                     # scan html files only
    --rule=/path/to/rule/file  # with specified rule file

'target' can be one file, files or folder(s)

output:
1. perfect (no fatals, warnings or notice)
    Congraturations! Your codes are very good.
2. with fatals, warnings or notice
    Total: 0 fatals, 1 warnings, 0 notice
    [fileN]
    F - R:C Rule-Message
    W - R:C Rule-Message
    N - R:C Rule-Message
    

